title: Car Rental
description: This Project is useful to rent a car. It has a user and admin panel. The user can book a car and the admin can add, delete and update the cars.

title: Currency Converter
description: This Project is useful to convert one currency to another. It uses the latest API to get the latest exchange rates.

title: Expense Tracker
description: This Project is useful to track your day to day expenses. it can add, delete and update your expenses.
